      <title>印度启动夏季燃气发电厂运行紧急规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/india-invokes-emergency-rules-to-run-gas-power-plants-for-summer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着电力需求开始上升，印度援引一项紧急条款，命令其闲置的燃气发电站在夏季运行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/india-invokes-emergency-rules-to-run-gas-power-plants-for-summer</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 09:07:54 GMT</pubDate>
